metadata.name: Fantastical Faces #634
metadata.description: 999-piece, one-of-one NFT collection featuring abstract geometry art as you've never seen before! Each piece is a unique, mesmerizing work of art that will transport you to another world. 2.5% of the creator fee will be donated to the charity of choice voted for on Twitter.I've been creating high geometry details and abstract art for more than 10 years now. My work has been praised for its attention to detail and the complexity of the designs I create. Every single piece I create is meticulously crafted, from the smallest detail, like a brush stroke or color changes, to more complex aspects such as the geometric shape of a flower or the various levels of abstraction present in an image. I'm passionate about expressing my creativity through both face painting and abstract art while pushing the boundaries of what's possible in the medium. With each new creation comes an opportunity to explore my imagination and express a unique story or emotion through my work.
